    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款中世纪魔幻风格的塔防策略游戏。玩家将在游戏中扮演王国的保卫者，保卫王国主堡不被哥布林军团摧毁。游戏中唯一消耗的资源就是玩家的光标操作时间，玩家可通过光标直接击杀哥布林或者建造和升级防御塔。合理建设不同功能的防御塔可以让玩家的防御阵线更加强大，配合光标杀敌，防御越来越强大的哥布林军团的进攻 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >光标右击消灭哥布林</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098320/extras/1145b0419e81212b1aa1904fcd9835ed.poster.avif?t=1761791967\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098320/extras/1145b0419e81212b1aa1904fcd9835ed.webm?t=1761791967\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098320/extras/1145b0419e81212b1aa1904fcd9835ed.mp4?t=1761791967\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>点点点点点点，防御哥布林军团的进攻，挥动你手中的光标！为保卫王国而战！！！！ </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >建造和升级防御塔</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098320/extras/cabcef592b8c2aed999a456ec9d50b86.poster.avif?t=1761791967\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098320/extras/cabcef592b8c2aed999a456ec9d50b86.webm?t=1761791967\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098320/extras/cabcef592b8c2aed999a456ec9d50b86.mp4?t=1761791967\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>游戏中设有多种不同功能的防御塔，玩家可通过光标操作来进行建造和升级，还可以通过升级王国主堡来解锁新的防御塔 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098320/extras/ee39db28cdabff6d9a30c7cd4bd22120.poster.avif?t=1761791967\" width=620 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098320/extras/ee39db28cdabff6d9a30c7cd4bd22120.webm?t=1761791967\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098320/extras/ee39db28cdabff6d9a30c7cd4bd22120.mp4?t=1761791967\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>不同种类的防御塔和自由布局操作为消灭哥布林军团和保卫王国主堡提供了更多的策略 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >哥布林军团的进攻</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098320/extras/ac0a501358d687cb16a7f86305433462.poster.avif?t=1761791967\" width=620 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098320/extras/ac0a501358d687cb16a7f86305433462.webm?t=1761791967\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098320/extras/ac0a501358d687cb16a7f86305433462.mp4?t=1761791967\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>游戏中会出现不同种类的哥布林，哥布林军团的进攻强度会随着时间的增长而愈发强力 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >哥布林军团将从各个方向发动进攻，玩家要尽可能地加强自己的防御阵线，保卫王国主堡抵御哥布林军团的进攻。加油！王国的保卫者！ </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌟  操作简单，只需使用光标即可完成所有操作，手速越快资源利用越充分</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌟  多种防御塔搭配使用，打造策略性十足的塔防防御机制，头脑风暴停不下来</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 🌟  特性各不相同的哥布林，组合成强大的哥布林军团分波次发动进攻，稳住我们能赢 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好了吗王国保卫者？哥布林军团已经抵达了王国边境，拿出你的勇气和信念，让我们一起战斗吧！！！ </p>",
